These are the release notes for the Spark extension.

Extension page on mediawiki.org: https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Spark
Latest version of the release notes: https://phabricator.wikimedia.org/diffusion/ESPK/browse/master/RELEASE-NOTES


=== Version 0.2 ===
==== 2011-10-16 ====
* Added CHANGELOG
* Added support for older versions of MW that do not have a resource loader
* Spark sometimes needs additional JavaScript. IT can be given in LocalSettings.php using the variable $wgResourceModules

==== 2011-0x-xx ====

* Added README, INSTALL, COPYTING and RELEASE-NOTES

=== Version 0.1 ===
==== 2011-05-30 ====

Initial release with these features:

* <spark> tag
